languages.description:
Trinity Homes are glad to offer you a spacious and well-maintained 4BR in Arabella 1 with Breathtaking views.

About Arabella

Located within the lush environs of Mudon, Arabella is a neighborhood that inspires good health and well-being among families. Stylish 3 and 4-bedroom townhouses nestle amidst vibrant greenery and boast an aesthetic that is clean and contemporary, while interiors are open, airy, and flooded with light.

Picturesque walkways draw residents through the community, past tranquil bodies of water to the expansive Mudon Central Park, which offers a wealth of leisure and sporting pursuits. A jogging track, sports courts, and exercise stations are complemented by children’s play areas and green open spaces that are perfect for picnics or barbecues.

The Arabella Mudon community has superb proximity to major highways including Emirates Road and Sheikh Mohammed Bin Zayed Road. The community also houses a community Centre, provides convenient retail and dining outlets, a children's nursery, a gym and fitness studio, as well as further fitness facilities for residents.
